1. 更改開機順序：
 (1) sudo gedit /etc/default/grub
 (2) sudo update-grub
     from：http://blog.xuite.net/lgn9999/blog/40158606-%E3%80%90%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8%E3%80%91ubuntu%E8%88%87windows+xp%E9%9B%99%E4%BD%9C%E6%A5%AD%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E9%96%8B%E6%A9%9F%E9%A0%86%E5%BA%8F%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9
2. 用root 權限編輯檔案：sudo nautilus
3. Ubuntu 雙系統安裝實錄：
   http://bruce30262.pixnet.net/blog/post/95082628-%5B%E7%9F%A5%E8%AD%98%2B%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%5D-win7-%2B-linux-mint-14.1-%E9%9B%99%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D%E5%AF%A6%E9%8C%84
4. disable asus touchpad：
 (1) 用xinput list 找出裝置 id
 (2) 輸入：xinput set-prop 12 "Device Enabled" 0  (ex：自己的laptop touchpad id 是14，12 的地方則換成14)
 (3) from：http://askubuntu.com/questions/65951/how-to-disable-the-touchpad
5. 安裝Lamp：
 (1) http://www.arthurtoday.com/2010/04/lamp-server-apache-mysql-php.html
 (2) http://it-easy.tw/ubuntu-lamp/
6. 安裝phpmyadmin：sudo apt-get install phpmyadmin
7. 解決phpmyadmin not found：
   Open apache.conf using your favorite editor, mine is vim :)
   sudo vim /etc/apache2/apache2.conf
   Then add the following line:
   Include /etc/phpmyadmin/apache.conf
   From:http://askubuntu.com/questions/387062/how-to-solve-the-phpmyadmin-not-found-issue-after-upgrading-php-and-apache
8. 安裝無蝦米：http://study2fun.blogspot.tw/2014/11/ubuntu-boshiamy.html
